77
00:03:28,942 --> 00:03:30,067
Kau hampir benar.

78
00:03:30,151 --> 00:03:33,192
Sepertinya kau di sini
untuk menyelamatkan tiga orang.

79
00:03:38,442 --> 00:03:40,109
Hai, Perawat...

80
00:03:40,484 --> 00:03:42,026
Perawat...

81
